{"tid":1622704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 三號幹線有人行緊","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T00:57:40.000Z","uid":54677,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f9aeff3d16c0905b6ccb3566d236aeca104c90","tid":1622704,"uid":54677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQpxr0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQpxr0C.jpg&h=15342192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌晒林奠同你所有班子老母同祖宗十八代<br />\n你見唔見撚到 呢度係三號幹線<br />\n一條時速行緊100KM嘅公路<br />\nd人行！緊！返！屋！企！<br />\n<br />\n係你 搞到香港風聲鶴唳<br />\n係你 搞到巴士小巴地鐵全停<br />\n係你 令香港人有家歸不得<br />\n<br />\n成個佐敦尖沙咀幾百人等緊車<br />\n大家安分守己返工敬業樂業<br />\n但你就徹底摧毀大家辛苦建立嘅家！<br />\n點解要搞到大家咁樣！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非 真心好想你哋行出嚟<br />\n每次只有勇武出嚟係無用<br />\n如果你哋唔出嚟 香港好快玩完<br />\n懇請你哋聽日後日都要出嚟<br />\n救下自己 救下香港<br />\n救下我哋呢頭家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b97f1c0f0a124609ef56fb496b765dc8861de86","tid":1622704,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"15cefaa8cb983e421996ba423f08e6f749478a2c","tid":1622704,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"咁你停底車左佢地未?"},{"pid":"0a290ec42278b579e0b94a6f026407ff60a45809","tid":1622704,"uid":54677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"15cefaa8cb983e421996ba423f08e6f749478a2c","tid":1622704,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"咁你停底車左佢地未?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"佢哋反方向行 我出去佐敦義載街坊"},{"pid":"38eef71ac1c719c5fd2f71fb867abd826bb1aacb","tid":1622704,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a290ec42278b579e0b94a6f026407ff60a45809","tid":1622704,"uid":54677,"like":4,"disli